snippet.title: Honey Grove - OUT NOW on the App Store and Google Play
snippet.description:
Honey Grove is a story driven gardening sim, out now for free on the App Store and Google Play! This game has no ads, only in-app purchases. 

Recruit a sisterhood of bees to join your hive and help revive the quaint woodland village of Honey Grove, all with the bountiful assistance of nature. 

🌸 Download now: https://onelink.to/honeygrove 

🌻 Discord: https://discord.gg/xyCvjRUHtW 
🌻 Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/honeygrovegame 
🌻 Twitter/X: https://x.com/honeygrovegame 
🌻 Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/honeygrovegame 
🌻 TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@runaway.games
